# This file exists only to make git track the reports/ directory.
# Git does not track empty folders; adding this placeholder ensures
# the reports/ directory appears in the repository so team members
# who clone the project have the correct folder structure.
#
# All HTML reports and PNG charts will be generated here when you run:
#   bruin run --asset reporting.generate_reports
#   bruin run --asset ml.evaluate_model
#   bruin run --asset ml.predict_traffic
